\id 1JN  
\h 1 John 
\toc1 John Lekhathot Khatna 
\toc2 1 John 
\toc3 1 Jn 
\mt1 JOHN  
\mt2 JOHN LEKHATHOT KHATNA  
\is1 Pathen to kiloikhomna dihtah  
\is1 Ngailut nachan bangin hingin!  
\is1 1 John lekhabu sung thu umdan  
\ip Pakai Jesu toh phatah a kivop chule Pakai Jesu thu hetgilna neipen chu Ngailut John hi ahi, ti geldoh in lang hiche lekhabu hi simpan in. Hiche lekhathot hi bung nga bou ahin, asunga thu umho jong asaove tia sei ding aumpoi. Pathen ngailutna neihon Thutah a hin ding phatah in hilna eineiyuve. Pathen cha ihi nung uva, leiset ihinkho uva Pakai to kiloikhom jing hinkho iti iman uva chule tahsan nei sopi dang ho toh jong iti hinkho iman diu ham, tithua hilna eineiyu ahi. Pathen hetgil chehna hinkho iti ineiyuva chule Ama ngailutna neiya vannoiya hi iti hinkho iman diu ham, tihi 1 John thudoi pipen ahi. Pathen I-Pauvin ichan geiya eingailut uva chule eihon jong Ama ichan a ingailut u ngai hintem, tithua phatah a hilna eineiyu ahi. Chule Ama ngailutna neihon Ama thenna hinkho ijuiyuva hinkho thenga hing ihi diu thudol eihil u ahi, \xt 1 Jn 3:1-3\xt*.  
\is1 Lekhathot jihpa chule ajih kum  
\ip Hiche lekhathot hi Solchah John'in (Gospel John jihpan) AD 85 leh 89 kichai kon lama ajih hidin ginchat ahi.  
\is1 Lekhathot kijihlona  
\ip John hin chuchelai phat a Ephesus khopi kimvel a Houbung ho (tua Turkey gamsunga um Houbung ho), chu tilkhouna le tahsanna'a hatsahna dinga ajih ahi.  
\ip Hichelai phat chun Rome Lenggam pumpia nam tampi ana umdoh in, chule thuneina lampang le kiloikhomna ho jong chu acham cham'a ana umdoh a chule kikan gahna ima ana umlou ahi. Hiti chun Nero Lengpan Christian te gimbol hesoh thohsah hi ahin panin, Christian ho chu mi asang-sang ana that in, Peter le Paul jong chu aman ana tha ahi. Hitobang tahsan ho gimbolna huipi le gopi kitho bang jeng chu chuche lai phat a Houbung umho le tahsan chate dinga hiche lekhathot hi Kongkai mun'a Thihhat kiseplha a kong kihen tobanga panga ahi.  
\c 1  
\s1 Hinna thu  
\p
\v 1 Keihon nangho kom'a kahillhang leu-atil abula pat a ana um jing, kanakol uva kajahsau, kamit uva kamusau chule kakhut uva kathamsau Hinna Thu chu ahi.\x + \xo 1:1 \xt Jn 1:1\x*  
\v 2 Ama tah hinna ahi chu keiho henga kiphongdoh ahitai chule keihon Ama chu kamu tauve, chule tua hi keihon ka hettohsah uva chule Ama tah Tonsot Hinna ahi tia kasei phongu ahi. Ama Pa toh ana umsa chujouva keiho henga hung kiphongdoh ah ahi.\x + \xo 1:2 \xt Jn 1:14\x*  
\v 3 Keiho tah in kamuchet uva chule kajahsau chu nangho henga kahillhangu ahin, hichu keiho toh ikiloikhom theina dingu ahi. Chule keiho toh kiloikhomna hi Pa le Achapa Jesu Christa toh kiloikhomna ahi.   
\s1 Pathen chu vah ahi  
\p
\v 4 Hiche ho chengse kajih uhi nang hon keihoa kipana nanei bulhing-chamkim theina dingu ahi.  
\v 5 Keihon Jesu a konna kajahsau thupoh chule tua naheng uva ka phondoh u chu hiche hi ahi-Pathen chu vah ahi, chule Ama a chu muthim umlouhel ahi.  
\v 6 Hijeh a chu eihon Pathen to kiloikhom kahi itiuva ahia lhagao muthim lah a vahle nalai ihiuleh eihon thutah chu juijing lou ihiu ahi.  
\v 7 Hinlah Pathen vah a aum banga vah a chu eiho ium uva ahileh, eiho khat le khat kiloikhom ihitauve, chule Achapa Jesu thisan chun ichonset nau jouse a konna eisil thengu ahitai.  
\v 8 Eiho chonsetna nei louva ikiseidoh uva ahileh eimaho tah kilhemlha ihiuvin, thutah a hinga ihi lou u ahi.  
\v 9 Hinlah eihon ichonset u Ama kom'a iphondoh uva ahileh, Ama chu ichonset nau ngaidam dinga tahsan um le kitah ahin, chule gitlouna jousea konna eisil theng theiyu ahi.  
\v 10 Eiho chonse khalouva ikiseidoh uva ahileh eihon Pathen jou seiya ingoh u chule Athu chun ilung uva mun aneilou ahi ti ivetsah u ahi.   
\c 2  
\s1 Eipanpiu Christa ahi  
\p
\v 1 Kacha deitahte, na chonset louna ding uva hiche hi naheng uva kahin jih ahi. Hinlah achonse aumtah a ahileh ichung thu u eiseicham peh thei dingu chonpha tah Jesu Christa chu inei nauve.  
\v 2 Ama tah hi ichonset nauva konna lhatdohna dinga hung kikatdoh a ahitai–chule eiho chonset jengseh hilouvin vannoi mite chonset jaljeh jong ahi.  
\v 3 Chule eihon Athupeh ho ijuiyuva ahileh Ama chu iheuve tia isei theiyu ahi.  
\v 4 Koiham khat touvin, Keiman Pathen kahei tihen Pathen Thupeh ho jui hih henlang hitaleh, ama tah chu mijou ahin, chule thutah a chu hing louva ahi.  
\v 5 Hinlah Pathen Thu jui a chu Ama ngailutna ivetsah tahbeh u ahi. Hichea hin Amaa hinga ihiuve ti ihetnau ahi.  
\v 6 Koi hileh Pathen a kahinge tiho chun Jesu banga abol diu ahi.   
\s1 Thupeh thah  
\p
\v 7 Deitahte, keiman nangho henga thupeh thah kajih ahipoi; atil abula naneisau thupeh lui chu kahin jih joh ahi. Hiche thupeh lui chu–khat le khat kingailut ding masanga najah sau chu ahi.\x + \xo 2:7 \xt Jn 13:34\x*  
\v 8 Hiche thupeh hi athah jong ahi. Jesu chu hiche thupeh a chon'ah ahin chule nangho jong hichea hi nachon diu ahi. Ajeh chu muthim hi hungmang ding chule vah tahbeh chu hungvah doh a ahitai.  
\v 9 Koiham khat touvin, “Keima vah a kavahlei,” tihen hinlah Christian asopi khat chu hotbol taleh, hiche pa chu muthim lah a um nalai ahi.  
\v 10 Koipen hijongleh sopi midang khat angailut a ahileh vah a chu chon'ah ahin, chule koima kipal lhuh sahlou ahije.  
\v 11 Hinlah sopi michom dang khat hot bola chu muthim lah a uma chule vahlea ahi. Hitobang mi chun achena ding lampi ahepon, muthim chun amit chotsah ahi.  
\v 12 Pathen chate ho dinga kajih ahi, ajeh chu Jesu jal'a na chonset u ngaidam nahi tauve.  
\v 13 Tahsan naa pilhing ho henga kahin jih ahi, ajeh chu atil abula pat a ana umsa Christa chu nang hon naheuve. Tahsana khangdong nangho henga kahin jih ahi, ajeh chu nang hon agiloupa chu na kidoupi uva najou ahitai.  
\v 14 Nangho Pathen chate ho henga kahin jih ahi, ajeh chu nang hon Pa chu naheuve. Tahsan'a pilhing nangho henga kajih ahi, ajeh chu nang hon Christa chu naheuvin, Ama chu atil abula anaum jingsa ahi. Tahsanna khangdong nangho henga kahin jih ahi, ajeh chu nangho nahat uvin chule Pathen thu na lungsung uva achenge, chule agilouto na kidouvu chu najou tauve.  
\v 15 Hiche vannoi hi ngailu hih un ahilouleh vannoiyin napeh u jong ngailu hih un, ajeh chu nang hon vannoi na ngailut tengu leh, nang hon Pa ngailutna chu naneilou u ahi.  
\v 16 Ajeh chu vannoiyin tahsalam lung ngaichat ho, mitmua deichat thei ho, chule ithilbol doh hou chule ineiho uva kiletsahpina apeh thei ahi. Hitiho hi Pa a kon ahipoi, ahin hiche vannoiya kon joh ahi.  
\v 17 Chule hiche vannoi le miho lung ngaichatna ho jong akem tul tul e. Hinlah Pathen lunglam bol ho chu tonsot a um jing ding ahiuve.   
\s1 Christa doupa akon kigahna  
\p
\v 18 Cha ngaitahte ho, phat nunung chu ahitai. Christa doupa ahunge ti naja tauve. Chule Christa dou tampi ahung kilangtai. Hichea kon hin phat kichai kon ahunghitai ti naheuve.  
\v 19 Hiche miho hin i-houbung hou adalhauve, hinlah amaho eihoto houbunga ium khom tahbeh khapouve, chuti lou hileh eiho toh umkhom diu ahitai. Adalhah u chun, amaho hi eihoa ahi pouve ti aphotchen ahi.  
\v 20 Hinlah nangho hitobang chun naum pouve, ajeh chu Lhagao Theng nachung uvah ahung tan chule nangho jousen thutah chu nahe sohkeiyuve.  
\v 21 Hichea keiman nangho kom'a kajih hi thutah nahe pouve tia kasei ahipon, ahin nang hon thutah le jouthu akibahlouna naheuve.  
\v 22 Chule koiham jouseipa chu? Koi hileh Jesu chu Christa ahipoi ti chan chu Christa dou ahi.  
\v 23 Koi hileh Chapa seilep chan chun Pa aneilou ahi. Hinlah Chapa phongdoh chan chun Pa chu anei ahitai.  
\v 24 Hitia hi, atil abula pat a nakihiluva chu tahsan umtah a napandet dingu ahi. Hichu nabol ahileh, nangma Pa le Chapa toh kiloikhoma nahi ding ahi.  
\v 25 Chule hiche kiloikhomna ithanop nau hi aman eithutep peh u Tonsot Hinna chu ahi.  
\v 26 Keiman hicheng thil ho kajih hi nangho napui lamvai ding hou chung chang thua nangho kagih nahiuve.  
\v 27 Hinlah nang hon Lhagao Theng naneiyuve chule Ama nangho sunga achenge chule ipi chu thutah ham tithua koiman nahil dingu ngaikhoh ahi tapoi. Ajeh chu Lhagao chun imalam jousea nahil dingu ahi, chule Aman ahil chu thutah ahi, Ama ah jou apangpoi. Hiti chun aman nahilsau bang chun, Christa to kiloikhomna nei jingun.  
\v 28 Chule tun, cha deitahte, Christa toh kiloikhomna neijingun, ajeh chu Ama ahung kilah tengleh nang hon lung ngamna bulhingset nanei dingu chule jahcha a chon talou ding nahiuve.  
\v 29 Eihon Christa chu chonpha ahi ti ihettah jeh uvin, koi hijongleh adih bola chu Pathen cha ahiuve tijong iheuve.   
\c 3  
\s1 Pathen chate  
\p
\v 1 Veuvin, Van'a um I-Pauvin ichan geiya eingailut u hitam? Ajeh chu Aman Achate tin eikou tauve–chule eiho jong ihi tahbeh u ahi! Hinlah hiche hi vannoiya hihon Pathen Chate ihiu hi ahepha pouve, ajeh chu ama hon Ama ahetlou jeh u ahi.\x + \xo 3:1 \xt Jn 1:12\x*  
\v 2 Ngaitahte ho–eiho Pathen chate ihiu ahitai. Chule ipi ihi dingu tun akilangdoh hih laiye. Hinlah eihon ihet u chu Christa ahung kilah teng chuleh eihon Ama ahina tahbeh a imu dingu ahitai.  
\v 3 Chule Ama hung ding kinem'a ngah jingho chu Ama athen banga amaho jouse jong thenga um ding ahiuve.  
\v 4 Koi hileh chonset bol chun Pathen Danthu apalkeh ahi, ajeh chu chonset jouse hi Pathen Danthu toh kikal ahi.  
\v 5 Koi hileh Ama toh hingkhom chu chonse jom louding ahiuve. Hinlah chonset boljom jing mi chu Ama heloulai ahilouleh Ama koi ahi hechen lou ahi.\x + \xo 3:5 \xt Jn 1:29\x*  
\v 6 Koi hileh Amaa um jom jing mi chu chonse louding ahi. Hinlah achonse jom jing chu koi hileh Ama chu heloulai ahilouleh hetkhenna neiloulai ahi.  
\v 7 Cha deitahte, hiche chung chang thu ah koiman nalhep lhah dauhen: Mihon adih tia ahol tengu leh, Christa chu chondih ahi banga amaho chondih a ahiuve ti avetsah ahi.  
\v 8 Hinlah miho chu achonset jom jing tengu leh amaho chu diabol a ahiuve ti avetsah ahi. Ama chu atil abula pat a ana chonse peh ahi. Hinlah diabol natoh ho sumang dinga Pathen Chapa hung anahi.  
\v 9 Pathen insung mia peng ho chun chonset aboljom jing pouve, Pathen a hinna chu amahoa um ahijeh ahi.  
\v 10 Hiti chun, tun koiho hi Pathen chate hiuva chule koiho chu diabol chate hiuvem ti iseithei tauve. Koi hileh chonphatna a hinglou ho chule midang tahsan chankhompi ngailulou ho chu Pathen a ahi pouve.   
\s1 Khat le khat kingailutna  
\p
\v 11 Hiche hi atil abula pat a nana jahsau chu ahi: Eiho khat le khat ikingailut dingu hi ahi.\x + \xo 3:11 \xt Jn 13:34\x*  
\v 12 Eiho Cain tobanga agilouva ihipouve, ama chun asopipa anatha ahi: Ipi jeh a atha hintem? Ajeh chu Cain chun aphalou abola chule asopipa chun chonphat abol jeh ahi.\x + \xo 3:12 \xt Semtilbu 4:8\x*  
\v 13 Hijeh chun, sopi deitahte, vannoiyin nahot uva ahileh datmo hih un!  
\v 14 Eihon Christian isopihou ingailut u ahileh, eiho thinaa konna hinna a galkai ihitauve. Hinlah ngailutna neilou chu athisa ahi.\x + \xo 3:14 \xt Jn 5:24\x*  
\v 15 Koi hileh sopi michom khat hotbola chu alungsunga tolthat ahitai chule tolthat ho chun asung uva tonsot hinna anei pouve.  
\v 16 Eihon ngailutna atahbeh ipiham ti iheuve, ajeh chu Jesun eiho dinga ahinna chu ahung pehdohsa ahitai.  
\v 17 Koiham khat chun sum neihen lang sopinu ahilouleh sopipan angaichat he henlang, hinlah khotona nei tahih leh–hiche pa chu Pathen ngailutna a iti um thei ding ham?  
\v 18 Kacha deitahte, eiho khat le khat ikingailu uve tin sei maimai pouhite, atahbeh chu ichonna uva vetsah u hite.   
\s1 Pathen angsunga kison  
\p
\v 19 Ichonna uvin thutah a hinga ihiu avetsah ding ahi, hitia chu Pathen masanga idin tengu leh lungngam tah a ium dingu ahi.  
\v 20 Ikithemmo channau aum jeng jongleh Pathen chu eimaho lunggel sanga lenjoa ahijeh in ijakai Aman ahet ahinai.  
\v 21 Kagol ngaitahte, eima hon kithemmo channa inei louva ahileh, Pathen kom chu lungngam tah a inailut theiyu ahi.  
\v 22 Chule ipi hijeng jongleh ithum chan u chu Amaa konna imu thei dingu ahi, ajeh chu eihon Ama sei ingai uvin, chule Ama lunglhaina chu ibolun ahi.  
\v 23 Chule hiche hi Ama thupeh ho ahi: Eihon Achapa Jesu Christa itahsan uva chule Aman eithupeh bang uva eiho khat le khat ikingailut dingu ahije.\x + \xo 3:23 \xt Jn 13:34; 15:12,17\x*  
\v 24 Pathen Thupeh ho nit a juiho chu: Ama toh kiloikhom ahiuvin, chule Ama jong amahoa chu uma ahi. Chule eihon eihoa Ama aum'e ti iheuve, ajeh chu Aman Lhagao eipeh u chu isung uva achengin ahi.   
\c 4  
\s1 Pathen Lhagao chule Christa dou lhagao  
\p
\v 1 Deitahte ho, Lhagaovin aseisah dana thuseiya kingaito koi koi hijongleh tahsan hih un. Nanghon amaho hung konna lhagao chu Pathen akon hinam ti patepna nei masauvin. Ajeh iham itileh themgao lhem tamtah vannoiya aumtai.  
\v 2 Hiche hi eihon Pathen Lhagao ineiyu kihetna ding ahi. Mikhat chu themgao hia akiseiya Jesu Christa chu tahsaphe le vou pun ahunge ti aphondoh a ahileh hiche mi chun Pathen Lhagao anei ahi.  
\v 3 Hinlah koi hamkhat chun themgao kahi tia akiseidoh a ahiala Jesu chung chang thudih chu aphondoh louva ahileh, hiche pa kiphondohna themgao kahi tia akisei chu Pathen a kon ahipoi. Hitobang mi chu Christa dou lhagao vannoiya hung ding ahi tia kisei najah u chule hichea hi uma ahitai ti nahetna ding uva ahi.  
\v 4 Hinlah nangho Pathen a nahiu ahitai, kacha ngaitahte ho, nang hon hiche mite hi najosau ahitai, ajeh chu nasung uva cheng Lhagao chu vannoiya cheng lhagao sanga chu lenjoa ahi.  
\v 5 Amaho chu vannoiya hiuva ahin, hijeh a chu vannoi lunggel lam thua aseidoh jiu ahin, chule vannoiyin aseiyu angaiyu ahi.  
\v 6 Hinlah eiho Pathen a ihiuve, chule Pathen heho chun eiho sei angaiyuve. Hiche hi mikhat chun thutah lhagao aneiham, ahilouva ahileh lheplhahna lhagao changa ham ti ihetnau ahiye.   
\s1 Khat leh khat ki ngaitlut ding  
\p
\v 7 Deitahte ho, eiho kingailu jom jingu hite, ajeh chu ngailut hi Pathen a kon ahi. Koi hitaleh ngailutna neija chu Pathen a kon ahi. Koi hitaleh ngailutna nei chu Pathen cha ahin chule Pathen ahei.  
\v 8 Hinlah koi hitaleh ngailutna neilou chun Pathen ahetlou ahi. Ajeh iham itileh Pathen chu ngailut ahi.  
\v 9 Pathen'in ichan geiya eingailut u hitam ti eivetsah nau chu Achapa chang khat seh chu vannoiya hi ahinsol ahitai, hitia chu Ama jal a eihon tonsot hinna inei theina dingu ahi.  
\v 10 Hiche hi ngailutna tahbeh ahi–eima hon Pathen ingailut u ahipoi, hinlah Aman eiho eingailut uva chule ichonset nau chu lahmangna dinga Achapa chu maichama ahin katdoh ahitai.  
\v 11 Deitahte ho, Pathen'in hichan geiya hi eingailut'u ahijeh in, eiho khat le khat ikingailut diu ahi.  
\v 12 Koimachan itih in jong Pathen amu khapoi. Hinlah eimaho khat le khat ikingailut touva ahileh Pathen chu eihoa uma chule Ami ngailutna chu eiho akiphondohna ihiu ahi.\x + \xo 4:12 \xt Jn 1:18\x*  
\v 13 Chule Pathen'in a Lhagao eipeh uhi eiho Ama a ihingun chule Ama eihoa aum'e, ti photchenna ahi.  
\v 14 Chukalval in, eima hon imit tah uvin imu uvin chule tun Pa chun Chapa hi vannoi huhhingpu dinga ahinsol ahi ti iphongdoh theiyun ahi.  
\v 15 Jesu hi Pathen Chapa ahi tia akama phongdoh ho chu asung uva Pathen chenga ahin, chule amaho Pathen a hinga ahiuve.  
\v 16 Eihon Pathen'in ichan geiya eingailut u hitam ti iheuve chule eihon angailutna tahsanna chu inei tauve. Pathen hi ngailut ahi chule ngailutnaa hing jouse chu Pathen a hinga chule Pathen asung uva uma ahi.  
\v 17 Chule eiho Pathen a ihin jeh uva, ingailut nau chamkim cheh na dinga khang khang jing ahi. Hitia hi thutanna nikhoa jong kichatna ineilou dingu ahi. Chusanga lung ngamna neiya Ama kimupina ineitheiyu ahitai, ajeh chu eiho hiche vannoiya hi Jesu tobanga ihinu ahitai.  
\v 18 Hitobang ngailutna hin kichatna aneipoi, ajeh chu ngailutna bulhingset chun kichat chu anodoh ahi. Eihon kichatna ineiyuleh gimbolna chan ding kichat jal ahi, chule hiche hin angailutna bulhingset in ihechen hih laiyuve ti avetsahna ahi.  
\v 19 Aman eingailut masat jeh uvin eihon Pathen'ingailu uve.  
\v 20 Koiham khat in, “Keiman Pathen kangailui,” ti hen, hinlah Christian sopi khat chu hotbol taleh, hiche pa chu mijou ahi, ajeh chu eihon imu theiyu miho ingailut louva ahileh, imu thei lou u Pathen chu iti ingailut dingu ham?  
\v 21 Chule Aman hiche thupeh hi eipeuve, hichu-Pathen ngailu hon a Christian chanpiu sopiho chu angailut dingu ahi.   
\c 5  
\s1 Tahsanna hi vannoi jousoh ahi  
\p
\v 1 Koi hileh Jesu chu Christa ahi ti tahsana chu Pathen cha ahitai. Chule koi hileh Pa ngailua chun achate jong angailut ding ahi.  
\v 2 Eihon Pathen ingailut uva chule athupeh ho init uva ahileh Pathen chate ingailu uve ti iheuve.  
\v 3 Pathen ngailut kiti hi athupeh ho nit hi ahi. chule athupeh ho chu pohgih ahipoi.\x + \xo 5:3 \xt Jn 14:15\x*  
\v 4 Ajeh chu Pathen chate tapou chun hiche vannoi gitlouna hi ajo ahitai, chule hiche jona chu itahsan jal'u ahi.  
\v 5 Chule hiche vannoi douna a kisatna hi koiyin ajo ding ham? Jesu hi Pathen Chapa ahi ti tahsan ho bouvin ajo ahi.  
\v 6 Chule Jesu Christa chu Pathen Chapa ahina kiphkonna chu twiya baptize channa le Thingpel chunga athisan sona jal jeh ahi, twisih jengseh a hilouvin, twi le thisan jal ahi. Chule Lhagao jong chun hichu a hettohsah in adih ahi ati.   
\s1 Pathen Chapa thudol hettohsah  
\p
\v 7 Hiti chun, eihon hiche hettohsahna thum ho hi ineiyuve–  
\v 8 Lhagao, Twi, chule Thisan–chule hiche thum ho hi khat ahiuve.  
\v 9 Eihon mihem hettohsahna itahsan uva ahileh, Pathen a konna hettohsahna chu iha tahsan cheh dingu hiya ahi. Chule Pathen'in Achapa thudol ahettohsah ahitai.  
\v 10 Pathen Chapa tahsan jouse chun alung sung uva hiche hettohsahna hi adih ahi ti itahsan uve. Hiche tahsan lou ho chun Pathen chu ajouve tia aseiyu ahi, ajeh chu Pathen'in Achapa thudol ahettohsah chu atahsan lou jeh u ahi.  
\v 11 Chule Pathen'in a hettohsahna chu hiche hi ahi: Aman tonsot hinna eipe tauve, chule hiche Hinna chu Achapa kom'a uma ahi.\x + \xo 5:11 \xt Jn 3:36\x*  
\v 12 Koi koi hileh Chapa neiya chun Hinna anei ahitai. Koi koi hijongleh Pathen Chapa neilou chun Hinna aneilou ahi.   
\s1 Tonsot hinkemlou hettheina  
\p
\v 13 Pathen Chapa min'a tahsan nangho henga hiche hi kahin jih ahitai, hichu Tonsot Hinna nei nahiu nakihetdohna dingu ahi.  
\v 14 Chule Aman ipi hijongleh alunglhaina hoa ithum chanu chu eingaipeh uve ti tahsanna ineiyuve.  
\v 15 Chule eihon ithum tengu leh Aman eingaipeh uve ti ihettah jeh uvin ipi hijongleh Aman eipeh dingu ahi tijong iheuve.  
\v 16 Nangman Christian sopi khat chun thina khop chonsetna hilou abol namua ahileh na taopeh ding ahi, chule Pathen'in ama chu ahinsah ding ahi. Hinlah chonsetna thina khop geiya bol'ah aum'e chule keiman chutobang bol ho dingin taovin kati ahipoi.  
\v 17 Gitlou bol jouse hi chonset ahi, hinlah chonset kitipou chun thina a apuilutpoi.  
\v 18 Eiho Pathen chaten chonset boljom jingna aneipoi ti iheuve, ajeh chu Pathen Chapan amaho chu akolchah a ahuhbit u ahi chule agiloupa chun amaho atong khapoi.  
\v 19 Eiho Pathen chate ihiuve chule vannoi ikimvel uva um hi agiloupa thuneina noiya uma ahi ti iheuve.  
\v 20 Chule Pathen Chapa chu ana hunga chule hetkhen themna chu eihungpeh u ahitai-chutia chu eihon Pathen dihtah chu ihettheiyu ahi ti iheuve. Chule tua hi eiho Pathen dihtah toh ihinkhom theiyu ahitai, ajeh chu eiho Achapa Jesu Christa toh kiloikhom ihitauve. Ama chu Pathen dihtah le tonsot hinna ahi.  
\v 21 Chapang deitahte, nalung uva Pathen mun lothei ding ipi hita jongleh hiche a kon chun kikhin mangun.   